ex:levels_of_contaminants_in_food_and_feed a skos:Concept ;
    skos:prefLabel "Levels of Contaminants in Food and Feed"@en ;
    skos:definition "A contaminant in food and feed is defined as any substance not intentionally added but present in such food or feed as a result of the production, manufacture, processing, preparation, treatment, packing, packaging, transport or storage, or as a result of environmental contamination, which can lead to major public hazards (FAO and WHO, 2019)."@en ;
    skos:prefLabel "Niveaux de contaminants dans les aliments et les aliments pour animaux"@fr ;
    skos:prefLabel "Niveles de contaminantes en alimentos y piensos"@es ;
    skos:prefLabel "Livelli di contaminanti negli alimenti e nei mangimi"@it ;
    skos:prefLabel "Рівні забруднюючих речовин у харчових продуктах і кормах"@ua ;
    skos:prefLabel "Уровни загрязнителей в пищевых продуктах и корме"@ru ;
    skos:prefLabel "食品和饲料中的污染物水平"@ch ;
    skos:prefLabel "Niveaus van verontreinigende stoffen in voedsel en veevoeder"@nl .
